# P8-001: List input (multi-file reads)

Accept `LIST(VARCHAR)` as the first positional argument of `read_pfile`,
`read_pgen`, and `read_pvar` so a set of variant-sharded pfiles reads as one
logical table. Motivated by biobank-scale sharding (chrom + K-megabase chunks)
and by `pathmacro:`/`pathfunc:` catalog resolution, which returns a `VARCHAR[]`
of shard prefixes.

